Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 12
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 12
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: The exploration of life on the nineteenth-century Silk Road continues. In this volume, meet Laila and Leily, identical twins on the search for husbands.
Title: A BRIDE'S STORY, VOL. 4
Author: Kaoru Mori

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 6
Author: James Patterson

Description: From the publisher: "Shigure learns Yukina's weakness: that she is terrified to have people look at her without her glasses on." What happens when he takes her glasses in front of some jealous girls?
Title: MISSIONS OF LOVE, VOL. 2
Author: Ema Toyama

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Naruto must battle an army of the undead controlled by Kabuto, who may also be controlling Itachi.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 58
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo regains his powers and learns a startling truth about himself.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 54
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: This is not your typical wonderland: Peter is a man with rabbit ears and Elliott March, the Mad Hatter’s enforcer, is a mafia hitman. How will Alice survive?
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS: MY FANATIC RABBIT, VOL. 1
Author: Quinrose

Description: Ritsuka is heartbroken over his brother’s death, but will the insight that Soubi, a mysterious, handsome college student, has make things any better?
Title: LOVELESS: 2-IN-1, VOL. 2
Author: Yun Kouga
